hadiths[15]{hadithnumber,text}:
1806,"Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) fasaad ke zamane mein Umra karne ke liye jab Makka janey lagey to aap ne farmaya ke agar mujhey Kaba sharif pahunchne se rok diya gaya to main bhi wahi kaam karunga jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ham logon ne kya tha, chunanche aap ne bhi sirf Umre ka ehram baandha kyonke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi Hudaibiya ke saal sirf Umre ka ehram baandha tha."
1807,"jin dinon Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) par Hajjaj ki lashkar kashii ho rahi thi to Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se logon ne kaha (kyonke aap Makka jana chahtey they) ke agar aap us saal Haj na karein to koi nuqsan nahi kyonke dar iska hai ke kahin aapko Baitullah pahunchne se rok na diya jaey. aap boley ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath gaey they aur kuffaare-Quraish hamarey Baitullah tak pahunchne mein haail ho gaey they. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni qurbani nehar ki aur sar mundaa liya, Abdullah ne kaha ke main tumhen gawah banata hun ke maine bhi inshaAllah Umra apne par wajib qarar de liya hai. main zaroor jaaunga aur agar mujhey Baitullah tak pahunchne ka rasta mil gaya to tawaaf karunga, lekin agar mujhey rok diya gaya to main bhi wahi kaam karunga jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya tha, main us waqt bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath maujood tha chunanche aap ne zul-Hulaifa se Umre ka ehram baandha phir thodi door chal kar farmaya ke Haj aur Umra to aik hi hain, ab main bhi tumhen gawah banata hun ke maine Umra ke sath Haj bhi apne uper wajib qarar de liya hai, aap ne Haj aur Umra donon se aik sath farigh ho kar hi dasween Zil-Hijja ko ehram khola aur qurbani ki. aap farmatey they ke jab tak haji Makka pahunch kar aik tawaaf ziyaarat na kar ley pura ehram na kholnaa chahiye"
1808,unse Naafe ne ke Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ke kisi betey ne unse kaha tha kash! aap us saal ruk jatey (to achchha hota usi uper waley waaqie ki taraf ishara hai).
1809,"Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse farmaya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Hudaibiya ke saal Makka janey se rok diye gaey to aap ne Hudaibiya hi mein apna sar mundwaayaa aur paak beeviyon ke paas gaey aur qurbani ko nehar kya, phir aainda saal aik doosra Umra kya."
1810,"ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) farmaya kartey they kya tumharey liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sunnat kafi nahi hai ke agar kisi ko Haj se rok diya jaey, ho sakey to wo Baitullah ka tawaaf kar ley aur Safa aur Marwa ki saee, phir wo har cheez se halal ho jaey, yahan tak ke wo doosrey saal Haj kar ley phir qurbani karey, agar qurbani na miley to roza rakhey, Abdullah se riwayat hai ke hamein Mamar ne khabar di, unse Zohri ne bayan kya ke mujh se Salim ne bayan kya, unse ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne usi pehli riwayat ki tarah bayan kya."
1811,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (suleh Hudaibiya ke mauqe par) qurbani sar mundwaaney se pahley ki thi aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ashaab ko bhi usi ka hukm diya tha.
1812,"Abdullah aur Salim ne Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se guftgu ki, (ke wo us saal Makka na jaaein) to unhon-ne farmaya ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Umre ka ehram baandh kar gaey they aur kuffaare-Quraish ne hamein Baitullah se rok diya tha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni qurbani ko nehar kya aur sar mundaayaa."
1813,"fitne ke zamane mein jab Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Makka ke iraadey se chaley to farmaya ke agar mujhey Baitullah tak pahunchney se rok diya gaya to main bhi wahi kaam karunga jo ( Hudaibiya ke saal ( maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath kya tha. aap ne Umre ka ehram baandha kyonke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi Hudaibiya ke saal Umra hi ka ehram baandha tha. phir aap ne kuchh ghaur karke farmaya ke Umra aur Haj to aik hi hai, iske baad apne sathiyon se bhi yahi farmaya ke ye donon to aik hi hain. main tumhen gawah banata hun ke Umra ke sath ab Haj bhi apne liye maine wajib qarar de liya hai phir (Makka pahunch kar) aap ne donon ke liye aik hi tawaaf kya. aap ka khayal tha ke ye kafi hai aur aap qurbani ka janwar bhi sath le gaey they."
1814,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya, ghaaliban juon se tum ko takleef hai, unhon-ne kaha ke ji haan ya Rasulullah! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir apna sar mundaa ley aur teen din ke rozey rakh ley ya chh miskinon ko khana khilaa de ya aik bakri zabah kar."
1815,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Hudaibiya mein mere paas aa kar khadey huey to juein mere sar se barabar gir rahi thin. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ye juein to tumharey liye takleef deh hain. maine kaha ji haan, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya phir sar mundaa ley ya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sirf ye lafz farmaya ke mundaa ley. unhon-ne bayan kya ke ye aayat mere hi barey mein nazil hui thi ke ''agar tum mein koi mareez ho ya uske sar mein koi takleef ho ''aakhir aayat tak, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya teen din ke rozey rakh ley ya aik farq ghalle se chh miskinon ko khana de ya jo muyassar ho uski qurbani kar de."
1816,"main Kab-bin-Ujra (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas betha hua tha, maine unse fidya ke barey mein puchha to unhon-ne kaha ke (qur'aan sharif ki aayat ( agarche khas mere barey mein nazil hui thi lekin iska hukm tum sab ke liye hai. hua ye ke mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein laya gaya to juein sar se mere chehrey par gir rahi thin. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (ye dekh kar farmaya) main nahi samajhta tha ke tumhen itni zyada takleef hogi ya (aap ne yun farmaya ke) main nahi samajhta tha ke mashaqqat tumhen us had tak hogi, kya tujh mein bakri (bataur fidya) dene ki taqat hai? maine kaha ke nahi, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir teen din ke rozey rakh ya chh miskinon ko khana khilaa, har miskeen ko aadha saa khilaanaa."
1817,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein dekha to juein unke chehrey par gir rahi thin, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha kya un juon se tumhen takleef hai? unhon-ne kaha ke ji haan, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein hukm diya ke apna sar mundaa lein. wo us waqt Hudaibiya mein they. (suleh Hudaibiya ke saal) aur kisi ko ye malum nahi tha ke wo Hudaibiya hi mein reh jaeinge balke sab ki khahish ye thi ke Makka mein dakhil hun. phir Allah Taala ne fidya ka hukm nazil farmaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya ke chh miskinon ko aik farq (yani teen saa ghalla) taqseem kar diya jaey ya aik bakri ki qurbani karey ya teen din ke rozey rakhey."
1818,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein dekha to juein unke chehre par gir rahi thi, phir yahi hadis bayan ki."
1819,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jis shakhs ne us ghar (ka'ba) ka Haj kya aur is mein na shahwat ki baat munh se nikaalii aur na koi gunah ka kaam kya to wo us din ki tarah wapas hoga jis din uski maan ne usey janaa tha.
1820,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jisne us ghar ka Haj kya aur na shahwat ki fahash baatein kin, na gunah kya to wo us din ki tarah wapas hoga jis din uski maan ne usey janaa tha."
